Marion Laine https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marion_Laine 0 Marion Laine is a French actor, screenwriter and film director. Her 2008 film A Simple Heart was entered into the 30th Moscow International Film Festival where it won the Special Jury Prize. Marion_Laine is a_French_actor_,_screenwriter_and_film_director .
